videos.headline: McCall gets rocked on TD as Coastal Carolina upends Kansas
videos.description: Grayson McCall escapes the pocket and takes a hit that sends him spinning in the air as he reaches the end zone to score a touchdown and give Coastal Carolina a 7-0 lead over Kansas.
